quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  74,18,"Mata-an! A sukaniyan na miyamimikiran go mithakdir,-"
  74,19,"Na Pimorka-an, andamanaya i kiyathakdir iyan!"
  74,20,"Oriyan niyan na Pimorka-an, andamanaya i kiyathakdir iyan!-"
  74,21,"Oriyan niyan na Miyangilai­lai,"
  74,22,"Oriyan niyan na Miyakari­mung, go komirus;"
  74,23,"Oriyan niyan na Tomiyali­khod go Miyanakabor;"
  74,24,"Na Pitharo iyan: A da ko ungkaya inonta na balik mata, a gi-i mithatanana;"
  74,25,"Da ko ungkaya inonta na Katharo o Manosiya!"
  74,26,"Pakasoludun Ko sukaniyan ko Naraka Sakar!-"
  74,27,"Na antawa-a i miyakandao Ruka o antona-a i Naraka Sakar?-"
  74,28,"A da-a Pulamba-an niyan, go da-a imbagak iyan!"
  74,29,"Puthotong ko kobal!"
  74,30,"Katatagowan sa sapolo a go siyao (a Malaikat)."
  74,31,"Na da-a tindo Ami a khito­tonggo ko Naraka a rowar ko man­ga Malaikat; go da-a kiyatundo Ami ko itongan niran a rowar sa tupung ko siran a Miyamangongkir; ka-an makatangkud so piyamugan ko Kitab, go an Makapagoman so Miyamaratiyaya sa Paratiyaya, go andi Kapaparampangi so piyamu­gan ko Kitab a go so Miyamara­tiyaya, go an Matharo o siran a kiyatagowan so manga poso iran sa Gudamun a go so Miyaman­gongkir: A antona-a i piyaka-anta­ pan o Allah sangkai a ibarat? Lagid man noto a kandadaga o Allah ko tao a kabaya lyan, go Kathoro a Niyan ko tao a kabaya lyan: Na da-a Mata-o ko manga tantara o kadnan Ka inonta Sukaniyan. Na da-a sal­akao saya a rowar sa Pananadum a ruk o Manosiya."
  74,32,"Di dun: lbut Ko Olan,"
  74,33,"Go so Gagawi-i igira-a Khai­pos,"
  74,34,"Go so Khapita igira-a Muli­wanag,-"
  74,35,"Mata-an naya! A titho a isa a mala,"
  74,36,"A lpuphamaka-ik tiyar ko Manosiya,-"
  74,37,"Si-i ko tao a khabaya rukano Mangonakona, o di na Puphapa­kaori."
  74,38,"Oman i ginawa na sanda ko Pinggalubuk iyan;"
  74,39,"Inonta so manga tao ko ka­wanan,"
  74,40,"Ka si-i ko manga Sorga, gi-i ran Pamagishai iyan,"
  74,41,"So manga Baradosa:"
  74,42,"Ino kano phakasolud ko Nar­aka Sakar?"
  74,43,"Isumbag iran: Da kami ma­baloi a pud ko manga Barasam­bayang,"
  74,44,"Go da kami mabaloi a Pu­phamugai sa Pangunungkun ko Miskin,"
  74,45,"Go miyabaloi kami a Pupha­murak, a pud o Puphamamurak,"
  74,46,"Go miyabaloi kami a gi-i yami pakambokhagun so Alongan a kapamalas,"
  74,47,"Taman sa Miyakatalingoma rukami so kapakatangkud (a giyoto so Kapatai)."